            "findingId/v1": "S-2"
          }
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/spoofing",
          "message": {
            "text": "An attacker may forge service identity tokens to impersonate the LLM Agent Orchestrator when communicating with the MCP Tool Server because inter-service authentication is not specified.",
            "markdown": "Enforce mutual TLS (mTLS) with certificate pinning between the LLM Agent Orchestrator and MCP Tool Server. Validate service identity claims using signed JWTs with RS256 and audience restriction."
          },
          "level": "error",
          "locations": [
            {
