          "partialFingerprints": {
            "primaryLocationLineHash": "a5e9eb30090af448",
            "findingId/v1": "S-4"
          }
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/spoofing",
          "message": {
            "text": "An attacker may perform DNS spoofing or MITM attack to redirect the MCP Tool Server's HTTPS requests to a malicious endpoint impersonating the External API.",
            "markdown": "Implement certificate pinning for the External API's TLS certificate. Enforce strict hostname verification. Use DNS-over-HTTPS resolver to mitigate DNS spoofing."
          },
          "level": "warning",
          "locations": [
